    <item>
      <title>苹果撤销欧盟禁止《堡垒之夜》制造商的举措</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/apple-reverses-move-to-ban-fortnite-maker-from-european-union</link>
      <description><![CDATA[面临欧盟监管机构越来越大的压力，苹果公司撤销了禁止《堡垒之夜》制造商 Epic Games Inc. 在该地区提供自己的 iPhone 应用市场的决定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/apple-reverses-move-to-ban-fortnite-maker-from-european-union</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 17:55:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台积电将为美国芯片厂赢得超过 50 亿美元的资助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/tsmc-to-win-more-than-5-billion-in-grants-for-us-chip-plant</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，台积电将赢得超过 50 亿美元的联邦拨款，以支持亚利桑那州的芯片制造项目，这将标志着乔·拜登总统振兴美国半导体制造业的努力的一个重要里程碑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/tsmc-to-win-more-than-5-billion-in-grants-for-us-chip-plant</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 17:14:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>OpenAI 的视频制作服务面临欧盟数据隐私审查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/openai-s-video-making-service-faces-eu-data-privacy-scrutiny</link>
      <description><![CDATA[OpenAI Inc. 面临意大利数据保护监管机构的进一步审查，原因是担心该公司的新人工智能视频创建系统会处理人们的个人数据。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/openai-s-video-making-service-faces-eu-data-privacy-scrutiny</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 16:03:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>快时尚店 Shein 将根据数字内容规则面临欧盟审查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/fast-fashion-shop-shein-set-to-face-eu-scrutiny-under-digital-content-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[快时尚公司 Shein 将受到欧盟旨在打击网上非法和有害内容的规定的影响，这表明监管机构正在更加密切地关注这家电子商务巨头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/fast-fashion-shop-shein-set-to-face-eu-scrutiny-under-digital-content-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 15:31:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯黑客正在将被盗的微软密码武器化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/russian-hackers-are-weaponizing-stolen-microsoft-passwords</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据微软公司称，一个由俄罗斯国家支持的黑客组织从微软公司高管那里窃取了敏感数据，并试图利用这些信息来破坏该公司的源代码和内部系统。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/russian-hackers-are-weaponizing-stolen-microsoft-passwords</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 15:10:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Nvidia 似乎已准备好在 1 万亿美元反弹后进行股票分割</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/nvidia-looks-primed-for-a-stock-split-after-1-trillion-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英伟达公司(Nvidia Corp.)的强劲上涨仅在今年就增加了超过1万亿美元的价值，远高于其上次拆股时的水平。一些人认为这家人工智能巨头有能力再次这样做。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/nvidia-looks-primed-for-a-stock-split-after-1-trillion-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 12:16:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其电池公司押注远离中国技术</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/turkish-lithium-battery-firm-kontrolmatik-bets-on-pivot-away-from-chinese-tech</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其 Kontrolmatik Enerji Ve Muhendislik AS 正计划利用国际债务市场并列出各种单位，以帮助为其在锂电池市场的扩张提供资金，因为该公司押注于对中国技术替代品的需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/turkish-lithium-battery-firm-kontrolmatik-bets-on-pivot-away-from-chinese-tech</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 11:49:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>博通软芯片销售下滑；期待人工智能推动增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/broadcom-chip-revenue-misses-estimates-even-as-ai-demand-grows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五上午，苹果公司和其他大型科技公司的芯片供应商博通公司公布其半导体业务收入令人失望，尽管该公司表示人工智能正在帮助推动需求，但该公司股价周五上午下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/broadcom-chip-revenue-misses-estimates-even-as-ai-demand-grows</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 21:22:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
